The paper deals with deep neural network models and their application to online learning and model-based reinforcement learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). Among these, machine learning and artificial intelligence are the most likely categories, as they are the most general and encompass a wide range of topics related to deep learning and online learning. Robotics and systems and control are also likely categories, as they are directly related to the application of these techniques to control and decision-making problems. Computer vision and pattern recognition is a less likely category, as it is not directly related to the main focus of the paper, but may be relevant if the paper includes visual perception or image processing tasks.
